<% content_for :titolo, "#{@pagina.titolo} - #{@pagina.numero}" %>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-6 bg-white font-mono"
     data-controller="exercise-checker page-viewer text-toggle font-controls"
     data-page-viewer-image-url-value="<%= asset_path('bus3_mat/p187/page.png') %>"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="card-selector">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        1
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Quale numero è formato da 3 unità, 2 migliaia e 4 centinaia?</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 ml-11">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q1" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>A.</strong> 3 240</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q1" data-card-selector-target="card" data-correct="true" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>B.</strong> 2 403</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q1" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>C.</strong> 2 430</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="card-selector">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        2
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Quale numero naturale è maggiore di 999 e minore di 1 000?</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 ml-11">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q2" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>A.</strong> 990</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q2" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>B.</strong> 1 001</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q2" data-card-selector-target="card" data-correct="true" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>C.</strong> Non esiste un numero naturale con queste caratteristiche</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="card-selector">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        3
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>In questa sequenza c'è un errore. Quale numero non è corretto?</strong><br>
        <span class="mt-2 block">1 003 • 1 006 • 1 009 • 1 012 • 1 051 • 1 018</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 ml-11">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q3" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>A.</strong> 1 009</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q3" data-card-selector-target="card" data-correct="true" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>B.</strong> 1 051</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q3" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>C.</strong> 1 018</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 4 -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="card-selector">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        4
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Sara ha 65 euro e sua sorella ha 15 euro in più. Quale operazione ti permette di scoprire quanto denaro ha la sorella di Sara?</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 ml-11">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q4" data-card-selector-target="card" data-correct="true" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>A.</strong> Addizione</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q4" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>B.</strong> Sottrazione</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q4" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>C.</strong> Divisione</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 5 -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="card-selector">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        5
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Marta acquista 5 pacchetti di caramelle, ogni pacchetto contiene 6 caramelle. Con quale operazione calcoli quante caramelle ha comprato Marta in tutto?</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 ml-11">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q5" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>A.</strong> 5 + 6</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q5" data-card-selector-target="card" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>B.</strong> 6 − 5</span>
      </label>
      <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer p-2 border border-gray-300 rounded hover:bg-yellow-50">
        <input type="radio" name="q5" data-card-selector-target="card" data-correct="true" class="w-5 h-5">
        <span><strong>C.</strong> 6 × 5</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer con controlli -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
